<plot>A New York Correspondent seeks information from both the North and South in order to understand the reasons leading up to Civil War. He discovers that six men have conspired to finance a renegade religious fanatic named John Brown. Brown raids a Federal arsenal at Harper's Ferry, Virginia. This Docu-drama is based on a true story as told by a ficticious character.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?107699</url></doc>
